## ğŸ“Š **3. BSS (Business Support Systems)**

Although emergency alerts are not commercial services, the **BSS subsystem still participates**:

### **BSS Responsibilities in This Useâ€‘Case:**

| Function                              | Role                                                                                       |
| ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Service Entitlement & User Groups** | Some alerts may be targeted (e.g., governmental users, critical infrastructure operators). |
| **Operational Reporting**             | KPI tracking of alert reach, delivery success, per-beam analytics.                         |
| **Resource/Cost Allocation**          | For government or agency customers of IRISÂ² secure services.                               |

### **Why BSS Matters**

3GPP identifies broadcast/multicast as important for public safety and operator service efficiency; integrating MBS with customer-facing and operational systems is necessary for accountability 
and service-level monitoring. [\[key4biz.it\]](https://www.key4biz.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iris2presentazione.pdf)

